  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/6705f370fb997054c7bf22c95b714a90.avif?t=1741132581\" width=516 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like cute anime girl characters? And want to practice your arithmetic skills? Then come here and have a relaxed math session with the girls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What? Can't calculate? Afraid of making mistakes? No worries, even if you get it wrong, it's okay! Keeping a relaxed mindset is the key!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/f3b1f93302b57dc812b43db70b6768b6.poster.avif?t=1741132581\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/f3b1f93302b57dc812b43db70b6768b6.webm?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/f3b1f93302b57dc812b43db70b6768b6.mp4?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the girls and answer addition or multiplication arithmetic problems, choose the correct option, and win the girls' hearts.You can also collect stickers to freely decorate your own  short, it's a very simple casual game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/52a63a1b848ef00b70ec54ce65eee388.poster.avif?t=1741132581\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/52a63a1b848ef00b70ec54ce65eee388.webm?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/52a63a1b848ef00b70ec54ce65eee388.mp4?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continuously answering correctly can trigger the \"Heart-throbbing Mode\" where no matter how you press, it's always correct!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The perfect combination of arithmetic and cute girls, the anime girls are charming and not lacking in cuteness, with a super refreshing answering mode, allowing everyone to get started quickly and exercise their arithmetic level. The game includes 6 girls with different personalities and a difficulty design that goes from shallow to deep, ensuring that you can play easily while also challenging your limits and becoming an arithmetic master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/570d4c24a9e8f6fa30e3135401c6bd63.poster.avif?t=1741132581\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/570d4c24a9e8f6fa30e3135401c6bd63.webm?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/570d4c24a9e8f6fa30e3135401c6bd63.mp4?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/6705f370fb997054c7bf22c95b714a90.avif?t=1741132581\" width=516 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like cute anime girl characters? And want to practice your arithmetic skills? Then come here and have a relaxed math session with the girls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What? Can't calculate? Afraid of making mistakes? No worries, even if you get it wrong, it's okay! Keeping a relaxed mindset is the key!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/f3b1f93302b57dc812b43db70b6768b6.poster.avif?t=1741132581\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/f3b1f93302b57dc812b43db70b6768b6.webm?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/f3b1f93302b57dc812b43db70b6768b6.mp4?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the girls and answer addition or multiplication arithmetic problems, choose the correct option, and win the girls' hearts.You can also collect stickers to freely decorate your own  short, it's a very simple casual game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/52a63a1b848ef00b70ec54ce65eee388.poster.avif?t=1741132581\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/52a63a1b848ef00b70ec54ce65eee388.webm?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/52a63a1b848ef00b70ec54ce65eee388.mp4?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continuously answering correctly can trigger the \"Heart-throbbing Mode\" where no matter how you press, it's always correct!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The perfect combination of arithmetic and cute girls, the anime girls are charming and not lacking in cuteness, with a super refreshing answering mode, allowing everyone to get started quickly and exercise their arithmetic level. The game includes 6 girls with different personalities and a difficulty design that goes from shallow to deep, ensuring that you can play easily while also challenging your limits and becoming an arithmetic master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/570d4c24a9e8f6fa30e3135401c6bd63.poster.avif?t=1741132581\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/570d4c24a9e8f6fa30e3135401c6bd63.webm?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376520/extras/570d4c24a9e8f6fa30e3135401c6bd63.mp4?t=1741132581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
